{"tid":2152042,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不如都支持下 肥佬黎 第一個親生仔 —- Giordano","createTime":"2020-08-11T17:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T21:15:17.000Z","uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16ad7c732778745380b1121499ede3ebed97b572","tid":2152042,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/佐丹奴\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%BD%90%E4%B8%B9%E5%A5%B4&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=737a0ff0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/佐丹奴</a><br />\n<br />\n1989年，中國六四事件期間，黎智英通過佐丹奴捐贈了20萬件恤衫給參加遊行的香港民眾支持民運。90年代，黎智英稱因其於六四事件的致力參與，特別在一封公開信尖銳批評國務院總理李鵬之後，佐丹奴所有位於內地的業務遭北京政府封殺，黎智英被逼將手頭上所有股份全部低價售出，自此專注發展傳媒事業，後逐漸把持有的佐丹奴股票出售，在2000年已經完全退出佐丹奴集團。<br />\n<br />\nGiordano啲生意都好唔掂<br />\n簡單啲買返一件白色T當支持下？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6839258f070c6dcbc5874de261bec67f8b6900","tid":2152042,"uid":223816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbaf707c60dccbb966eac47c272c5a79f5c17d4","tid":2152042,"uid":14478,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc47eedb55a48ec0cb1970a28a963fc7c83f6c4","tid":2152042,"uid":92340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:35:02.000Z","msg":"冇晒股份都支持係咪玩法"},{"pid":"cf72c1581d4aefa3ea0ab7197d706117222c0b24","tid":2152042,"uid":197005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"219631c42525a0783744a05d7ed49500a6e5ebc0","tid":2152042,"uid":71085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfef0f12f